NK079(dzu)001:1: // ba dz+ra sa t+wa m+aa y+aa dz+aa lam ta n+t+ra
NK079(dzu)001:2: s+ya t+ai ka kh+y+aa tam s+aa d+ho p+aa yasu k+sh+m+aa
NK079(dzu)001:3: n+aam pra kri y+aa d+ai paka&a&a&a ra b+h+aan+aa ma sti
NK079(dzu)001:4: ///rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rgyud kyi
NK079(dzu)001:5: 'grel bshad dang sgrub thabs phra mo'i dkar chag gsal
NK079(dzu)001:6: byed snang ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK079(dzu)001:7: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)001:8: rigs bdag phrin las rgya mtsho'i gter //
NK079(dzu)001:9: phan bde'i 'byung gnas la btud de //
NK079(dzu)001:10: des bshad sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba yi //
NK079(dzu)001:11: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud sde las //
NK079(dzu)001:12: pan grub 'jig rten mig gyur pa'i //
NK079(dzu)001:13: legs bshad 'grel sgrub rnams kyi gzhung //
NK079(dzu)001:14: rnam grangs gsal byed snang ba'i dpal //
NK079(dzu)001:15: don gnyer pad+mo'i gnyen du spro //
NK079(dzu)001:16: de yang lta ba dang mtshan ma med pa'i ting nge 'dzin ston pa'i skor la /
NK079(dzu)001:17: dga' rab kyi la shan lta ba'i sgron me rtsa 'grel /
NK079(dzu)001:18: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi lta ba rnam bkod /
NK079(dzu)001:19: klu sgrub kyi g.yu yi thang ma skras dgu /
NK079(dzu)001:20: pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi lta ba'i phreng ba rtsa 'grel /
NK079(dzu)001:21: sh+r+ai sid+ha'i thugs kyi sgo lcags /
NK079(dzu)001:22: bde ba gsal mdzad kyi theg pa chen po shes rab kyi rim pa /
NK079(dzu)001:24: bee ro tsa na'i bstan pa'i snying po /
NK079(dzu)001:25: ska ba dpal brtsegs kyi lta rim snang ba bcu bdun pa /
NK079(dzu)001:26: d+har+m+aa b+ho d+hi'i bkol mdo rnams so //
NK079(dzu)001:27: 'di dag ni theg pa kun gyi lta grub ston
NK079(dzu)001:28: pa'i phyir theg pa spyi la 'jug pa'i man ngag
NK079(dzu)001:30: gzhan yang bi ma la'i mtshan nyid sgron ma /
NK079(dzu)001:34: shes rab spyan 'byed rtsa 'grel rnams so //
NK079(dzu)001:35: dz+ny+aa na'i 'phrul gyi me long dgu skor rtsa 'grel /
NK079(dzu)001:36: bod kyi pan+di ta a tsar+ya gnyan dpal dbyangs kyi sgron ma drug pa rnams so //
NK079(dzu)001:39: lta ba yang dag sgron ma /
NK079(dzu)001:41: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa'i sgron ma /
NK079(dzu)001:42: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i lungs nges pa'i don la ji bzhin sgom thabs /
NK079(dzu)001:43: lta ba rin po che'i sgron ma rnams so //
NK079(dzu)001:44: gzhan yang mtshan med sgom thabs gtso bor ston pa'i gzhung la /
NK079(dzu)001:45: bi ma la'i spyod yul bzhi ba'i bsam gtan /
NK079(dzu)001:46: spyod yul sbyong ba'i bsam gtan /
NK079(dzu)001:47: rnam par mi rtog pa'i sgom lung /
NK079(dzu)001:48: ting nge 'dzin sgron me'i bsam gtan /
NK079(dzu)001:49: rig pa sgron me'i bsam gtan /
NK079(dzu)001:50: yan lag bzhi pa'i bsam gtan h'u nyid rol pa'i man ngag rnams so //
NK079(dzu)001:51: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i sems don bsdus pa'i bsam gtan /
NK079(dzu)001:54: dur khrod bde ba'i rmi lam gyi man ngag n+ri don rnam par sbyong ba rnams so //
NK079(dzu)001:55: rgyud bshad thabs kyi skor la /
NK079(dzu)001:56: rgyud kyi spyi'i don bshad pa'i khog dbub ni /
NK079(dzu)001:57: sgeg pa rdo rje'i thugs thigs spyi gcod /
NK079(dzu)001:58: bi ma la'i khog gzhung gsal ba'i sgron me /
NK079(dzu)001:59: khog gzhung gsal sgron bye brag bstan pa 'od kyi snang ba /
NK079(dzu)001:60: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba gsal ba'i
NK079(dzu)001:61: me long zhes pa'i man ngag zab mo kun las
NK079(dzu)001:62: btus pa / lo ts+aa ba chen po rin chen mchog gi bshad thabs bcu pa la sogs pa'o //
NK079(dzu)001:64: rtsa rgyud la sgeg pa rdo rje'i rin po che'i spar khab /
NK079(dzu)001:66: nyin byed seng ge'i rgyal cher 'grel /
NK079(dzu)001:67: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i rnam dbye /
NK079(dzu)001:68: pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi rnam bshad chen mo //
NK079(dzu)001:69: slob dpon tsan+da go mi'i rgya mdud 'grel rnams yin la /
NK079(dzu)001:70: lo ts+aa ba chen po bee ro tsa na'i 'grel
NK079(dzu)001:71: pa yang yod ces grags pa sgyu 'phrul bla ma
NK079(dzu)001:72: chen po la bi ma la'i mun sel sgron ma
NK079(dzu)001:73: / le'u lag la bi ma la'i spyan rnam par 'grel pa /
NK079(dzu)001:74: brgyad cu pa la bi ma la'i bsdus 'grel /
NK079(dzu)001:75: lo pan chen po gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes kyi mngon par rtags pa'i rgya cher 'grel /
NK079(dzu)001:76: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo'i phreng ba la pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi don bsdus pa'i 'grel pa /
NK079(dzu)001:77: bi ma la'i 'grel pa rnams so //
NK079(dzu)001:78: yang rtsa rgyud le'u nyer bzhi pa kha che'i pan+di
NK079(dzu)001:79: ta a nan+ta sh+r+ai'i 'gyur la don gsal bar byed
NK079(dzu)001:80: pa'i rgya cher 'grel pa zhes bya ba rgya 'grel
NK079(dzu)001:81: rnam dag snang bas a nan+ta'i yin nam snyam /
NK079(dzu)001:82: sgrubs thabs phra mo'i skor la /
NK079(dzu)001:83: rgyud kyi dngos po bdun nam dagu'am bcu la sogs
NK079(dzu)001:84: par phye yang 'dir slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i
NK079(dzu)001:89: phrin las te lngar gsungs pa ltar byas na /
NK079(dzu)001:91: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi dbang du byas te /
NK079(dzu)001:92: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi chos don mdor bsdus par bstan pa /
NK079(dzu)001:93: bi ma la'i thig gi pin+d+aar+tha /
NK079(dzu)001:94: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i zhi ba rdo rje las kyi
NK079(dzu)001:95: rim pa dang khro bo rdo rje las kyi rim
NK079(dzu)001:96: pas ni dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba dang dbang gi
NK079(dzu)001:97: las rim thun mong du bstan la /
NK079(dzu)001:98: 'og nas 'byung ba'i gcig spros tshogs sgrub rnams kyi
NK079(dzu)001:99: skabs nas kyang gzugs brnyan gyi bya ba ci rigs
NK079(dzu)001:100: par ston no // dbang la dzi na mi tra'i
NK079(dzu)001:101: sems bskyed cho ga nam mkha'i snying po'i sems bskyed
NK079(dzu)001:102: par ston no // / bi ma la'i bsre ba'i las rim /
NK079(dzu)001:104: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i las rim gnyis ni gong du
NK079(dzu)001:105: bstan la zhi ba rdo rje las rim la bi
NK079(dzu)001:107: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dbang gi don nges par 'byed pa /
NK079(dzu)001:108: lo ts+aa ba rma rin chen mchog gi nges 'byed
NK079(dzu)001:109: che ba rnams ni dbang bco brgyad spyi'i dgongs pa
NK079(dzu)001:110: yin la / gtso bor zab dbang gsum gyi dgongs 'grel la /
NK079(dzu)001:111: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i galpo rtsa 'grel /
NK079(dzu)001:112: rdo rje gro bo lod kyi galpo'i 'grel pa mi 'jigs phreng ba /
NK079(dzu)001:113: sgeg pa rdo rje'i thugs thig rtsa 'grel /
NK079(dzu)001:114: de la dzi na mi tra'i 'grel pa rin chen snang ba /
NK079(dzu)001:115: sgeg pa'i lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes snang ba /
NK079(dzu)001:118: gsang thigs rtsa 'grel dbang gcig char du 'jug pa'i man ngag /dbang rgyud pa rtsa 'grel /
NK079(dzu)001:119: rna rgyud rdo rje zam pa /
NK079(dzu)001:120: brgyud pa snying gi sgron ma /
NK079(dzu)001:122: gzhan lus shes rab kyi 'khor lo //
NK079(dzu)001:123: bde ba chen po phyag rgya'i man ngag /gtum mo'i me dbang che chung gnyis /
NK079(dzu)001:124: sgrol ma rlung gi man ngag rnams so //
NK079(dzu)001:125: yang in+da b+hu ti'i rin chen 'khor lo /
NK079(dzu)001:126: ye shes zhabs kyi ye shes snang ba /
NK079(dzu)001:127: rin chen phreng ba gsum ni gsar ma'o //
NK079(dzu)001:129: sgeg pa rdo rje'ii bsrung bya'i dmigs gtso bor bstan pa gsal bkra /
NK079(dzu)001:130: rnam grangs gtso bor ston pa phra rgyas /
NK079(dzu)001:131: bshags pa gtso bor ston pa rgyun bshags /
NK079(dzu)001:132: slob dpon s+thi ra ma ti'i grangs dang bshags thabs
NK079(dzu)001:133: thun mong du bstan pa nyi shu rtsa brgyad pa
NK079(dzu)001:135: bi ma la'i srung thabs gtso bor ston pa mchod rten ris /
NK079(dzu)001:139: khrus lung rgyal mtshan rnams so //
NK079(dzu)001:140: kun dga' snying po'i nyes dmigs gtso bor ston pa gcan 'phrang chen mo /
NK079(dzu)001:143: sgrub pa'i gtso bo ting 'dzin pas //
NK079(dzu)001:144: zhes sgrub pa ni gtso bor ting 'dzin yin la /
NK079(dzu)001:145: de'i yan lag tu ji ltar bya ba'i lag len 'byung ba yin no //
NK079(dzu)001:146: ting nge 'dzin dngos la mtshan ma dang bcas pa'i
NK079(dzu)001:147: ting nge 'dzin dang mtshan ma med pa'i ting nge
NK079(dzu)001:148: 'dzin gnyis kyi dang po la'ang mchog bsgrub pa'i ting
NK079(dzu)001:149: nge 'dzin yan lag rgyas pa dang /
NK079(dzu)001:150: thun mong sgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK079(dzu)001:151: dang po zhi ba'i phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin la /
NK079(dzu)001:152: bi ma la'i phyag rgya bsam gtan //
NK079(dzu)001:153: de la jo bo sangs rgyas kyi 'grel pa //
NK079(dzu)001:154: bi ma la'i lha sku mngon snang //
NK079(dzu)001:155: phyag rgya bzhi ba'i bsam gtan /
NK079(dzu)001:156: khro bo la bi ma la'i phyag rgya gcig pa che chung gnyis /
NK079(dzu)001:157: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i he ru ka sku gsung thugs kyi sgrub thabs /
NK079(dzu)001:158: khro bo phyag rgya bsam gtan /
NK079(dzu)001:159: bi ma la'i rtse gcig bsdus pa'i bsam gtan //
NK079(dzu)001:160: yi dam lha'i chos chung rtsa 'grel //
NK079(dzu)001:163: bi ma la'i zhi ba rgyas pa'i sgrub thabs 'od kyi rim pa /
NK079(dzu)001:165: me long lta bu'i sgrub thabs dzi na mi tra'i rgyud don gsal byed /
NK079(dzu)001:166: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i 'bring po'i sgrub thabs rin che d+r+wa chung /
NK079(dzu)001:167: 'di la bi ma'i 'grel pa yod do //
NK079(dzu)001:168: bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs bi ma la'i slob ma rgyal
NK079(dzu)001:169: ba bzang po dpal gyi zhi ba 'od kyi phyag
NK079(dzu)001:170: rgya / khro bo la dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i sgrub
NK079(dzu)001:171: thabs bi ma la'i he ru ka las kyi phreng
NK079(dzu)001:172: rgya / ba / 'bring po'i sgrub thabs khro bo yang dag sgron ma /
NK079(dzu)001:173: bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs shes rab sgron ma /
NK079(dzu)001:174: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs snang ba dam pa rgyan /
NK079(dzu)001:175: de'i 'grel pa bi ma las mdzad pa'o //
NK079(dzu)001:176: tshogs sgrub kyi lag len ston pa la /
NK079(dzu)001:177: sgyu 'phrul tshogs kyi lag len ston pa sgyu 'phrul tshogs kyi 'khor lo bi ma las mdzad pa /
NK079(dzu)001:178: sgrub pa'i yan lag tshogs mchod skor la /
NK079(dzu)001:179: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i rnal 'byor gtor ma'i rim pa /
NK079(dzu)001:181: dur khrod bde ba'i za tshogs gtor lung /
NK079(dzu)001:185: bi ma la'i thabs mchog dpag gis mi lang ba /
NK079(dzu)001:186: dbyig gi sgron ma la sogs pa'o //
NK079(dzu)001:187: thun mong gi sgrub pa ni /
NK079(dzu)001:189: rkang mgyogs mig rnon la sogs pa thun mong sgrub
NK079(dzu)001:190: pa bzhi bcu zhe gcig sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa las
NK079(dzu)001:191: bshad de de dag la man ngag gi yi ge
NK079(dzu)001:192: zur du bkol ba ma mthong ngo //
NK079(dzu)001:193: mtshan med kyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK079(dzu)001:194: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba dang /
NK079(dzu)001:195: ting nge 'dzin dngos gnyis su 'gyur la /
NK079(dzu)001:196: de dag re re nas kyang khong 'brel du 'byung
NK079(dzu)001:197: bas phyogs gcig tu byas te gong du bstan zin
NK079(dzu)001:198: to // zhi khro thun mong la /
NK079(dzu)001:199: bi ma la'i zhi ba'i rtog pa'i lha rgyud 'grel pa dang bcas pa /
NK079(dzu)001:200: khro bo'i rtog pa'i lha rgyud 'grel pa dang bcas pa /
NK079(dzu)001:201: cho ga bsdus pa'i sgron ma /
NK079(dzu)001:202: nam mkha'i snying po'i zhi khro'i las kyi gal phreng /
NK079(dzu)001:203: de nyid nyi shu rtsa dgu pa'o //
NK079(dzu)001:204: bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka ston pa'i gzhung /
NK079(dzu)001:205: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i bskyed rdzogs kyi man ngag slob
NK079(dzu)001:206: dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa lo ts+aa ba
NK079(dzu)001:207: lcog ro la sogs pa gsum gyis bsgyur ba /
NK079(dzu)001:208: in+da b+hu ti'i rim pa gnyis pa /
NK079(dzu)001:209: bi ma la'i rim pa gsum pa /
NK079(dzu)001:211: de la dz+ny+aa na'i 'grel pa yod do //
NK079(dzu)001:213: sgeg pa rdo rje'i rim pa drug pa /
NK079(dzu)001:214: de la bi mi la'i 'grel pa rin chen phra bkod /
NK079(dzu)001:215: rgyud kyi dngos po rdzogs par ston pa'i gzhung sangs
NK079(dzu)001:216: rgyas gsang ba'i lam rnam par bkod pa zhes bya
NK079(dzu)001:217: ba lam rim che ba 'di la lo tsa ba
NK079(dzu)001:218: bran kha mu rti'i 'grel pa yod /
NK079(dzu)001:219: bi ma la'i sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i lam bshad pa
NK079(dzu)001:220: r+ya rin mchog gis mdzad zer ba'ang snang zhes lam
NK079(dzu)001:221: rim chung ba / in+da b+hu ti'i lam rnam par bkod pa la sogs pa'o //
NK079(dzu)001:223: sgrol ba'i gnas las bya ba /
NK079(dzu)001:224: dur khrod bde ba'i gnas kyi mdo byang /
NK079(dzu)001:225: bi ma la'i tshig rkang bcu dgu pa /
NK079(dzu)001:226: gnubs kyi lung phra mo bcu drug la /
NK079(dzu)001:229: tshe 'das kyi rnam par shes pa 'gugs pa'i lung phran /
NK079(dzu)001:230: rnam par shes pa dgug pa'i gtan tshigs kyi lung phran /
NK079(dzu)001:231: thugs rje chen po sbyang ba'i lung phran /
NK079(dzu)001:232: thabs shes mda' gzhu'i lung phran /
NK079(dzu)001:233: mchod rten gdab pa rus chog gi lung phran /
NK079(dzu)001:234: h'u nyid ring por spar ba'i lung phran rnams ni bi ma las mdzad /
NK079(dzu)001:237: sbubs 'jug bshig pa rnams pad+mas mdzad /
NK079(dzu)001:238: sa lam lung phran dz+ny+aa nas /
NK079(dzu)001:239: bcol dang skong ba bi ma las /
NK079(dzu)001:243: ro sreg gi cho ga slob dpon dpal gyi ye shes kyis mdzad pa /
NK079(dzu)001:244: gnas kyi gegs sel gzer bco brgyad pa rnams dz+ny+aa nas /
NK079(dzu)001:245: dur khrod bde ba'i dpe chung rang gnas /
NK079(dzu)001:246: de la 'grel pa bi ma las /
NK079(dzu)001:247: dur khrod bde ba'i phrin las rol pa'i sgrub thabs /
NK079(dzu)001:250: bsreg pa me'i sgo nas las bya ba /
NK079(dzu)001:251: bi ma la'i sbyin sreg gi rim pa mdor bsdus pa /
NK079(dzu)001:253: lu gu rgyud kyi las rim /
NK079(dzu)001:255: mnan sreg thun mong ba rnams so //
NK079(dzu)001:256: gdab pa mchod rten gyi sgo nas las bya ba /
NK079(dzu)001:257: bi ma la'i rab gnas las rim /
NK079(dzu)001:259: rgyal ba bzang po'i rab tu gnas pa'i rtsa ba rnams so //
NK079(dzu)001:260: gzhan yang kha skong phra mo'i skor la /
NK079(dzu)001:261: cha gsum dpal rdom ma'i tho byang khu drong gis mdzad pa /
NK079(dzu)001:262: brjod med kyi bshags pa gnubs sangs rgyas kyi kha skong ba /
NK079(dzu)001:263: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dam tshig nyer brgyad pa'i bshags pa /
NK079(dzu)001:264: grub thob dpal dbyangs kyi 'gro ba'i don phyir /
NK079(dzu)001:266: khro rgyal dpal chen rnams so //
NK079(dzu)001:267: dkyil 'khor lha rgyud kyi smon lam bkra shis rab mchog la sogs pa rnams so //
NK079(dzu)001:268: de ltar sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba yi 'grel sgrub lo pan mkhas pa'i gzhung /
NK079(dzu)001:269: brgyad dang zhe bdun 'grel pa bcu pa ni /
NK079(dzu)001:270: drug cu rtsa gcig bcu phrag bcu /
NK079(dzu)001:271: 'dir ni lta ba rgyud bshad dam /
NK079(dzu)001:272: dbang dam sgrub pa phrin las skor //
NK079(dzu)001:273: kha skong rnams su bsdus te bstan //
NK079(dzu)001:275: gang zhig 'dir slar yang gsum bsnan yod /
NK079(dzu)001:277: phyogs su bgrod pa'i yid rmongs te //
NK079(dzu)001:278: 'grel sgrub mtshan tsam shes pa'ang da kon //
NK079(dzu)001:279: de phyi gsung rab nam mkha'i yid bzhin nor //
NK079(dzu)001:280: rnam grangs gsal byed shing rtas legs drangs nas //
NK079(dzu)001:281: blo gsal yid kyi kun gsal la bkod kyis //
NK079(dzu)001:282: snga 'gyur bstan pa'i pad tshal rgyas par mdzod //
NK079(dzu)001:283: ces pa 'di yang rig sngags 'chang ba se'i ban+de
NK079(dzu)001:284: rin chen rgyal mtshan dpal bzang pos dpal ldan rgya
NK079(dzu)001:285: mkhar gyi yang dben du bris /
